			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
					<h1>Komma i kontakt</h1>
					<p><strong>WhygencyGravity</strong><br/>Birger Jarlsgatan 18<br/>114 34 Stockholm<br/>Sverige</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<a href="http://www.facebook.com" title="Facebook" target="blank">
